    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is an ideal choice for someone looking for a dependable daily driver without the high price tag of a newer model. While the engine and transmission are in good working order, the car does show its age with some visible scratches on the exterior and noticeable wear on the interior upholstery. It has been regularly serviced, though it may soon require some minor maintenance to keep it running smoothly. Overall, it's a solid, functional car that prioritizes utility over appearance.",
