    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting with my trusty ride and it's looking for a new adventure. It's been super reliable and is in great shape for its next owner. Perfect for weekend trips or just getting around town with a smile. It's been well-loved, runs beautifully, and is ready to hit the road today!",
