    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking for a new home for my awesome car! It\u2019s been super reliable and is still in really great shape, perfect for your daily commutes or weekend adventures. It\u2019s been well-loved and drives smoothly, so you can just hop in and go! Honestly, it\u2019s a fantastic find for anyone wanting a solid, dependable ride. Can\u2019t wait for you to see it!",
