    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "This 951-generation Porsche 944 Turbo features the iconic M44/51 2.5L inline-four, utilizing a KKK K26 turbocharger that delivers linear boost across the powerband. The front-engine, rear-transaxle layout provides a near-perfect 50/50 weight distribution, connected by a rigid torque tube for exceptional torsional stiffness. This example remains mechanically robust, with the interference-valve timing assembly recently serviced and the four-piston Brembo fixed-caliper braking system providing firm, fade-resistant deceleration. The suspension retains its factory-spec MacPherson struts and rear semi-trailing arms, offering precise turn-in and analog feedback. A well-sorted driver\u2019s car for the technical purist.",
